ces.docker_service import DockerService\n  Line 39:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py:\n  Line 11: from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\n  Line 38:         self.docker_service = DockerService()\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/docker_service.py:\n  Line 15: class DockerService:\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-024 — DockerService 封装 Tasks\n  Line 3: **AR:** AR-024  \n  Line 12: ### Phase 1: DockerService Helper Methods\n  Line 13: - [ ] **T001** Implement `_format_size(size_bytes: int) -> str` method in DockerService (AR-024-006)\n  Line 14: - [ ] **T002** Implement `_get_image_info(image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]` internal method with size formatting (AR-024-003-C)\n  Line 15: - [ ] **T003** Implement `_docker_login_sdk(registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str)` helper method (AR-024-007)\n  Line 16: - [ ] **T004** Implement `_tag_image_sdk(source_image: str, target_image: str)` helper method (AR-024-008)\n  Line 18: ### Phase 2: DockerService Return Value Updates\n  Line 19: - [ ] **T005** Update `build_image` return dict to include `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time` (AR-024-002)\n  Line 20: - [ ] **T006** Update `get_image_info` return dict to include `created` field (AR-024-003-A)\n  Line 21: - [ ] **T007** Update `push_image` return dict to include `pushed_image`, `push_time` (AR-024-004-A)\n  Line 22: - [ ] **T008** Update `push_image` to handle image retagging for registry URLs (AR-024-004-C)\n  Line 25: - [ ] **T009** Add Docker availability check in PackRuntime before Dockerfile generation (AR-024-010-A)\n  Line 29: - [ ] **T011** Add DockerServic