kerService API in delta-spec *(the spec itself exists in `changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md`)*\n\n---\n\n**Note**: The core implementation is functionally complete. The deferred items are primarily additional test coverage and documentation refinements that could be addressed in a follow-up iteration.","time":{"start":1775865636204,"end":1775865636204}}}
